        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued September 15 at 2:27PM MDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 227 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Lovington, moving north at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph and pea size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Lovington.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
